article.description: — Taze Moore had 18 points, seven rebounds, four assists and three steals to help CSU Bakersfield beat Cal Poly 67-50 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Moore scores 18, CSU Bakersfield beats Cal Poly 67-50
article.linkText: Moore scores 18, CSU Bakersfield beats Cal Poly 67-50
article.story: BAKERSFIELD, Calif. -- — Taze Moore had 18 points, seven rebounds, four assists and three steals to help CSU Bakersfield beat Cal Poly 67-50 on Saturday night. De'Monte Bukcingham had13 points, Justin Edler-Davis 12 and Justin McCall scored 11 for Bakersfield (7-4, 3-1 Big West Conference). Camren Pierce led Cal Poly (2-6, 0-2) with 12 points and Colby Rogers added 11. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
